	(text "Fix this:\n\nUse buck boost from battery to 5.2V\n\n5.2V -> ferrite bead -> ulta low noise LDO -> 5V \n\nRefine the power supply, know what voltage is needed for the DAC\n\nThe amp likes low noise 5V, but will make its own noise, use TPS7A20\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 171.704 19.812 0)
		(effects
